snippet.title: DEEP STATE - Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
DEEP STATE is a first person shooter inspired by classic games such as Goldeneye 007, Deus Ex, and Resident Evil.

Frogman Interactive is a two person team developing DEEP STATE in their spare time. If you’d like to help quicken the pace of development please consider supporting the project by following the links below. 

Wishlist the game on STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2788210/DEEP_STATE/?utm_source=youtubetrailer
Download the demo on itch.io : https://frogmandev.itch.io/deep-state
Download the demo on indieDB: https://www.indiedb.com/games/deep-state
Come chat with us on Discord: https://discord.gg/DfxQxmWSsR
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/deepstategame
